[I] Tablet description library

[T] libwacom is a library to identify graphics tablets and their model-specific
[T] features. It provides easy access to information such as "is this a
[T] built-in on-screen tablet", "what is the size of this model", etc.

[U] https://github.com/linuxwacom/libwacom

